Class ES1KeyGen

java.lang.Object
org.openlca.io.ecospold1.input.ES1KeyGen
public class ES1KeyGen extends Object
Generator for name-based UUIDs (version 3) for EcoSpold 01 entities.

See http ://openlca.org/documentation/index.php/UUIDs_for_EcoSpold_01_data_sets.
